quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  34,46,"Nena, “Ine ndili kukufunsani kuti muchite chinthu chimodzi choti muime pamaso pa Mulungu awiriawiri kapena aliyense payekha ndipo muganize painu nokha. M’bale wanu si wamisala ayi. Iye ali kungokuchenjezani chilango chowawa chisanadze.”"
  34,47,"Nena, “Malipiro ena aliwonse amene ndidakufunsani ndi anu chifukwa malipiro anga ali ndi Mulungu ndipo Iye ndi mboni pa zinthu zonse.”"
  34,48,"Nena, “NdithudiAmbuye wanga amanena zoona ndipo ndi Mwini wodziwa zinthu zobisika.”"
  34,49,"Nena, “Choonadi chadza ndipo bodza latha ndipo silidzabwereranso.”"
  34,50,"Nena, “Ngati ine ndilakwa, ndilakwira mzimu wanga ndipo ngati ndatsatira njira yolungama ndi chifukwa cha zimene Ambuye wanga amavumbulutsa kwa ine. Ndithudi Iye amamva ndipo ali pafupi.”"
  34,51,Ndipo iwe ukadangoona nthawi imene adzachite mantha komabe iwo sadzathawa ndipo iwo adzagwidwa asanapitepatali
  34,52,"Ndipoiwoadzati,“Ifetilikukhulupirira.” Kodi kukhulupirira kwawo kudzawathandiza bwanji kuchokera kutali"
  34,53,Ndipo iwo sadakhulupirire kale ndipo amanena kuti ndi nkhani za m’maluwa kuchokera kutali
  34,54,Ndipo chipupa chidzakhazikitsidwa pakati pawo ndi zofuna zawo monga momwe adachitira ndi anthu ena a kale. Ndithudi iwo ndi okayika kwambiri